Description.value:
Abusiness ServiceNow iflow delivers a sample interface for creating tickets in the Service Now application, and any sender can consume the Dost Add-On. ServiceNow Access variable is externalized (SNOW_OAuth) and can be maintained by the user in security artifacts (SNOW_OAuth). (XML Schema is provided below).

<JIRATicket>
	<Action>CREATE</Action>
	<ProjectId>12345</ProjectId>
	<Summary>SnowTicket handler | </Summary>
	<Description>Bad Request : 400 : HTTP/1.1 Grouping BP01 has external number assignment, enter a number</Description>
	<Assignee>undefined</Assignee>
	<IssueType>Bug</IssueType>
	<SprintNum>1137</SprintNum>
	<Reporter>dostaddon</Reporter>
</JIRATicket>
